<P>Several ACTS AND LAWS Passed by the Great and General Court or Assembly of Their Majesties Province of the Massachusetts-Bay, in NEW ENGLAND.</P>
<P>Convened and Held at <HI>Boston,</HI> the Eighth Day of <HI>June.</HI> 1692.</P>
<P>Anno Regni Gulielmi, et Mariae. Regis et Reginae Angliae, Scotiae, Franciae, et Hiberniae, Quarto</P>
<P>BOSTON, Printed by <HI>Benjamin Harris,</HI> Printer to His Excellency, the Governour and Council. 1692.</P>
</DIV1>
